\end{verbatim}
Structure to store the time and frequency parameters for the FFT analysis

\textbf{Constructor}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{fs::Real}: Sampling rate of the signal


\item \texttt{bs::Real}: Block size of the signal


\item \texttt{pow2::Bool}: Flag for finding the next power of 2

\end{itemize}
\textbf{Fields}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{t::AbstractRange}: Time vector


\item \texttt{dt::Float64}: Time step


\item \texttt{tspan::Tuple\{Float64, Float64\}}: Time span


\item \texttt{freq::AbstractRange}: Frequency vector


\item \texttt{df::Float64}: Frequency resolution


\item \texttt{freq\_span::Tuple\{Float64, Float64\}}: Frequency span


\item \texttt{fs::Int}: Sampling rate


\item \texttt{bs::Int}: Block size

\end{itemize}

